creator: Desoutter Mobile
descriptionHtml:
The Desoutter Assistant app features all the latest innovations by Desoutter. Find a complete product catalog, an accessory configurator or all our documentation, and easily get in touch with our experts worldwide!
• Discover the full Desoutter catalog and bookmark your tools
• Talk to Lisa, our chatbot, to find the right accessory for your tool.
• Access all technical data, documentation and product catalogs/leaflets
• Watch videos presenting our products, our company, or Industry 4.0 topics...
• Easily send a photo and a message to one of our experts around the world
• Available in 19 languages

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
What's new:
• New interface and navigation redesign! Our team is very excited to release a fully redesigned navigation.

What's also fixed:
• Opening a chat photo in fullscreen mode
• "Partial" status in "Order Tracking"
• Import/Export functions in "Service Value Calculator "
• "Converters" keyboard fix on iOS devices
• Updated translations

We release updates regularly to make our app better and easier to use. Please share your experience by leaving a comment!
